// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0843 — Mass File Rename (akira)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 69a68c6f-de89-513e-8357-3a05eebeeac2

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
